      <div class="demo-area demo-area--col">

        <div class="brand-qa">
          <h3 class="aboutMe">What does the company do?</h3>
          <p class="aboutMeText">
            E-Quipi is an online store specializing in premium gaming peripherals for PC and console
            players. The company sells desk mats, mice, mechanical keyboards, controllers, and
            ergonomic accessories designed for both performance and aesthetics. The website helps
            users browse products by category, view detailed product specifications, compare options,
            purchase items, and leave reviews after their purchase.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="brand-qa">
          <h3 class="aboutMe">Who is the company to potential customers?</h3>
          <p class="aboutMeText">
            If E-Quipi were a person, it would be a knowledgeable friend who has an incredibly
            clean, well-optimized desk setup and always knows exactly which gear is worth buying.
            The brand is precise, tasteful, and no-nonsense — it does not oversell or use hype,
            but speaks confidently about quality and craft. It feels less like a big-box electronics
            retailer and more like a trusted specialist who helps customers build a setup they are
            genuinely proud of.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="brand-qa">
          <h3 class="aboutMe">Why might this company entice someone to purchase?</h3>
          <p class="aboutMeText">
            E-Quipi may entice customers because every product page goes beyond basic specs to
            explain how the product fits into a real setup — surface texture, feel, size, and
            compatibility are all considered. The clean visual presentation and honest product
            descriptions build trust, and the curated product selection means customers are not
            overwhelmed with low-quality options. The focused range signals that everything in
            the store has been chosen deliberately.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

